{"tid":658783,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"而家d細路好有衣食🤔撈麵跌左落地下執番照食,😰","createTime":"2018-05-09T09:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T13:17:49.000Z","uid":67869,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5049466a301b96de666f6b91d56043ab79865e","tid":658783,"uid":67869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:15:50.000Z","msg":"話說頭先口痕去左買tea食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾個小學生（大約7-9歲）一人買左一個撈麵食<br />\n其中一個接左個面係咁撈<br />\n撈撈下連紙碗帶麵sir左落地, 碗側著地<br />\nD面有大約5cm x 8cm掂左個地<br />\n個o靚仔同佢兩個friend加我望住呆左<br />\n跟手佢執番, 再同佢d friend講, 照食啦<br />\n<br />\n見佢食得津津有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/171216_1b0532c149ac8b42dfcba76743624f70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F171216_1b0532c149ac8b42dfcba76743624f70.jpg&h=53a1bb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw...題外話,細細個已經用支付寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24af0616e51247851fd12ff3c3a91767aeb35763","tid":658783,"uid":97226,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"細路冇錢係咁咖啦 on99關你撚事"},{"pid":"129b9201f3b4871cc9ed3e73129a25e6cd4b7e74","tid":658783,"uid":133350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"細路都已經咁有衣食，樓主應該lam幹淨埋佢"},{"pid":"e322546ef174dd6c4c659625c489c13e394315a7","tid":658783,"uid":133350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"129b9201f3b4871cc9ed3e73129a25e6cd4b7e74","tid":658783,"uid":133350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"細路都已經咁有衣食，樓主應該lam幹淨埋佢"},"citedBy":0,"re